## PoiTable.load() method

Start to load the PoiTable from the specified URL. Can only be called once per table.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
load(poiTableUrl: string): Promise<boolean>;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  poiTableUrl | string | URL that points to the JSON file. |

<b>Returns:</b>

Promise&lt;boolean&gt;

{<!-- -->Promise<boolean>} Promise is being resolved once the JSON file has been fetched and the `PoiTable` has been set up.
